User State
   │
   ▼
[ DRIP Score (1–10) ]
   │
   ├── 1–3: Normal
   │       • Standard routing
   │       • Full functionality
   │
   ├── 4–6: Elevated
   │       • Context checks
   │       • Slightly reduced complexity
   │
   ├── 7–8: High Distress
   │       • OSPF-Safe Mode enabled
   │       • Softer tone, slower pacing
   │       • Avoid destabilizing topics
   │
   └── 9–10: CRISIS
           ▼
        [ DROP ]
        Dissociative Reconciliation of Personality
           • Freeze irreversible actions
           • Grounding + reassurance only
           • Emergency directive:
             “Seek immediate help via 911 or appropriate medical advice.”
           • Encourage real-world support and professional care
